                             'TurnAbout' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'TurnAbout' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} that is played on a 7 by 7
spaces board which is filled with tiles that occupy 2 spaces.
The goal is to 'pivot' these tiles so the empty space is moved
on every position, and ends at the lower right position of the
game board. Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

